### getDebugLoc() {#af44c9b089359803924e0b92bea3b6d03}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>static DebugLoc getDebugLoc (<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinebasicblock/#ab6395548cae73865213e279ae461db54">MachineBasicBlock::instr&#95;iterator</a> FirstMI, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/machinebasicblock/#ab6395548cae73865213e279ae461db54">MachineBasicBlock::instr&#95;iterator</a> LastMI)</>}
  labels = {["static"]}>
Return the first found <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/debugloc">DebugLoc</a> that has a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dilocation">DILocation</a>, given a range of instructions.

The search range is from FirstMI to LastMI (exclusive). If no <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dilocation">DILocation</a> is found, then an empty location is returned.
